javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3060">SCP-3060</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4160">SCP-4160</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1260">SCP-1260</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1360">SCP-1360</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3460">SCP-3460</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3560">SCP-3560</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4660">SCP-4660</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1760">SCP-1760</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2860">SCP-2860</a>/<a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3860">SCP-3860</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2960">SCP-2960</a>/<a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3960">SCP-3960</a></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>Now the planets have aligned, and the great old ones shall return. May their coming cleanse the world.</p> <p>Anyway, enjoy the article.</p> <p><em>JC</em></p> 
